Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,红宝石们?\NThe Rubies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:27.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈?哇!\NHuh? Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦，天哪!\NOh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啊!\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-是你!-爱宝!\N-You!-Eyeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.66,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,地球拜拜\NThere goes the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我的整个团都拜拜了好吗!\NThere goes my whole platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:47.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,简直一团糟!我该怎么写进报告里?!\NThis is a mess!What'll I say in my report?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我能不能写报告都成问题!\NHow will I even{\i1}make{\i} my report?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,简直噩梦!\NThis is a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:55.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,全都是你的错!\NAnd this is all{\i1} your{\i} fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等等，不，才不是!\N-Whoa!-Hey, no, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是你先要伤害我的朋友的!\NYou were trying to hurt my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:03.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是打开月面基地气阀的人是你!\NBut you opened the airlock in the moon base!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:07.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是你把我们送进了太空--\NYou sent us flying into space --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:09.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还根本没有回家的希望!\Nwith no hope of ever returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧，也许那个是我的错\NOkay, so maybe that was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对不起-现在高兴了吧?\NI'm sorry.There, are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不高兴\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,要不是你被泡泡保护着\NYou're lucky you're in that bubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我就一拳打在你脸上\Nor I'd pop you right in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,行啊，你要是一直这么无理取闹\NWell, if you're going to be a grump about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们就直接在太空里白头偕老得了!\Nthen we can just float in silence until we both die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:29.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-听起来不错-行!\NSounds great.Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我都等不及去死了!\NI can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我也等不及!\NMe, neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:47.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?没信号?\NWhat? No signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.66,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,拜托，旁边不就有颗卫星吗?!\NCome on,I'm right by a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,如果我没在这里死掉\NIf I don't die out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,回地球第一件事就是换个手机套餐\Nfirst thing I do back on Earth is change my phone plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:58.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我就不应该回到这颗蠢星球来!\NI shouldn't have ever come back to that dumb planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当我听说地球上可能还有水晶战士的时候\NWhen I heard rumors there might still be Crystal Gems on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:04.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我当时都没敢相信\NI couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一千年的战争都徒劳无功!\NA thousand years of fighting were all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:11.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,再想想玫瑰石英可能还活着?\NAnd Rose Quartz might still be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她肯定还活着\NShe must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:15.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不然为什么铁石英那么重要的人物\NWhy else would someone as important as Jasper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:16.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,会回来地球呢?\Nbe back on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当然是为了确认玫瑰是否活着\NFor closure, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我也这么想过\NI wanted it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:25.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我也想亲眼看看玫瑰石英\NI wanted to see Rose Quartz with my own eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,至少\NAt the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以为铁石英会有答案，可...\NI thought Jasper might have some answers, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:34.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那根本不是她--只是另一个把戏\Nit wasn't even her --just another trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:38.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这才是你真正想要的?想看看玫瑰石英?\NThat's what you really wanted?To see Rose Quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,比什么都想\NMore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那么-今天就是你的幸运日了\NWell, then today's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,怎么讲?\NHow's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:49.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我知道玫瑰石英在哪\Nknow where Rose Quartz is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?她在哪?\NWhat? Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她变成了我\NShe turned into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你要是她\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还有两只眼呢\NAnd I have two eyeballs --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你看看我有吗?\Nwhich I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你真的以为我蠢到什么都信，是吧?\NYou expect me to believe anything, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,耍我一次，我丢人\NFool me once, shame on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:09.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,耍我四次，真的算是耍了我了\NFool me four times,you already fooled me --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:12.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我绝不会再上你的当\Nand you can't fool me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:13.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你不相信我的话，我可以证明!\NLook, I can prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我身上有她的宝石!\NI have her Rose Quartz gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这宝石看着红中带粉\NThat's more of a pinkish-red
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:20.52,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,玫瑰石英的宝石可是粉中带红\Nthan a real Rose Quartz reddish pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那是因为你隔着我的泡泡在看啊!\NThat's because you're looking at it through my bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下...\NHold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,来，看这个!\NHere, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看，我能召唤她的盾牌!\NLook,I can summon her shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:31.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你看上面还有玫瑰啥的\NIt's got a rose on it and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谁管她的盾啊?\NWho cares about her shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:37.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我只记得她有粉色的巨剑\NHer huge sword is what I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:41.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃，我把剑丢在狮子那里了\NUh, I left that in my lion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:46.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看看我身上有没有玫瑰的影子\NTell me you don't see the resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:52.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你在逗我?你可真卑鄙\NAre you kidding me?You're despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们都要死在这儿了\NWe're gonna die out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:56.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你还要在临死前开我的玩笑\Nand you're just gonna make fun of me until we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:01.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你真是比玫瑰石英还残忍\NYou're even crueler than Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:07.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃，爱宝?\NUh, Eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,爱宝?!\NEyeball?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那不是我弄的...\NThat's not my --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,简直不能再棒!\NOh, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,小行星袭来!\NAsteroids incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,士兵，各找掩护!\NFind cover, soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我已经有掩护了，你倒是找地方躲啊!\NI am in cover,you get somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇!\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,感觉筋骨没年轻时灵活了\NI think I'm losing my luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们要撞上那块大的了!\NWe're heading right for that big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦?\NOh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还活着\NI'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们做到啦!\NWe made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我是无敌的!\NI'm unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,爱宝!\NEyeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:51.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦，不，不!\NOh, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我抓到你了\NI've got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:00.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦天了!你还好吗?\NOh, geez! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:02.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,起开!\NGet off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇，你怎么了?\NWhoa!What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀!你的宝石开裂了!\NAy-yi-yi!Your gem is cracked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?还能再倒霉点吗?!\NWhat?!This is just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别担心--我能修复你的宝石!\NDon't worry --I can fix your gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:20.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我才不会信你的鬼---话!\NI'm not falling for any of your tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我是认真的--我能帮你\NI'm serious -- I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,死马当活马医好了\NI guess I got nothing else to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,欸?!\NEh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你这是要干啥?!\NWhat was that supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,天儿了你脑袋里都在想...\NWhat in the cosmos is wrong with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,什么?\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.68,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看，成功了!\NSee? It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.74,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我简直不敢相信!\NI can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,过去战场上有个流言--\NThere were rumors back during the war --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:06.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,流言说玫瑰石英能够治愈水晶战士们\Nthat Rose Quartz could heal her Crystal Gem soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,把自己的小军队\Nkeeping her small army
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:11.82,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,打造得能与母星的强大军事力量匹敌\Nin contention with the superior forces of Homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇哦，真的是你!\NWow!It really is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,玫瑰石英!\NRose Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,现在信了吧?!我一直都在证明这一点!\NSee?! That's what I was trying to tell ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:24.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对，就是我--伟大的玫瑰石英!\NYup, it's me --the mighty Rose Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,现在我们被困在这里\NAnd now we're stuck out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:31.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,向宇宙中漫无目的地漂流\Nfloating aimlessly through outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噗\NPff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们是怎么把自己搞到这般田地的?\NHow'd we get ourselves into this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,伟大的玫瑰石英\NThe mighty Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,做梦都想不到我会有这种机会\NI never thought I'd get a chance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,想不到你会败在我手下!\NI can't believe you're all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?!\NWah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你为啥要攻击我?!\NWhy are you attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:11.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别假装惊讶了，玫瑰石英!\NDon't act surprised,Rose Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你碎掉了一颗钻石!\NYou shattered a Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:17.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇!\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,吼吼，我要抓到你啦!\NOoh, I'm gonna get ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我要拿到你的宝石带回母星!\NI'm gonna take your gem and bring it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?!不!不要拿走我的宝石!\NWhat?! No!Please don't take my gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下，拿走宝石以后我会怎么样啊?\NWait, what would even happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-哈?-嗯?\N-Huh?!-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈!\NHa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:41.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等-等下!你不必这样做的!\NW-Wait!You don't have to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:44.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦，快点认输吧!\NOh, give it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你不会再糟蹋我这次机会了!\NYou can't take this away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我将会成为一个传说!\NI'm gonna be a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我会名留青史!\NI'll go down in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我红宝石打败玫瑰石英\NWhat will the Diamonds say when they hear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,听了这之后钻石她们会怎么想呢?\Nthat a Ruby defeated Rose Quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们会奖励给我一个专属的珍珠!\NThey're gonna give me my own pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?\NWah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下!听我说!\NWait! Please listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我真的不是我妈妈!\NI'm really not my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不想伤害你!\NI don't want to hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你-你要三思啊\NJust --Just think for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们已经迷失在太空了\NWe're lost out in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么自己回母星?\NHow are you going to get back to Homeworld alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我已经拿定主意了\NI've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.66,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.51,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ If I could ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Begin to be ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Half of what you think of me ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ I could do about anything ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:34.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ I could even learn\Nhow to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ When I see ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ The way you act ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Wondering\Nwhen I'm coming back ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ I could do about anything ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:46.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ I could even learn\Nhow to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Like you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:56.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.52,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为什么没有人跟我讲过粉钻的事情?\NHow come nobody told me about Pink Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,战争期间我们做了很多不得已的事\NWe all did what we had to during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.52,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是现在一切都已经变了\NEverything's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是妈妈真的那么做了吗?\NBut did mom really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:09.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她真的粉碎了粉钻吗?\NDid she really shatter her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她也不得已\NShe had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,地球以前是粉钻的\NThe Earth belonged to Pink Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,摧毁粉钻是拯救地球的唯一出路\NDestroying her was the only way to save the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为了紫晶能选择自己命运，为了珍珠能不受束缚\NFor Amethyst to be herself,for Pearl to be free,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为了我能在一起\Nfor me to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为了你能存在\NFor you to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是我以为...\NBut I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.51,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,至少她绝对不会...\Na-at least she'd never...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:30.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她的选择并不只为了她自己的利益\NShe didn't always do what was best for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:33.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她做的一切都是为了地球\NBut she always did what was best for Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:37.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,甚至不惜粉碎一个宝石\NEven if it meant shattering someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们能告诉我\NThanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:53.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Love me like you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
